data.description: Located close to US 19 in Pinellas Park, this home is perfect for a quick commute to work. Features include 1259 sq ft of Living Space consisting of 3 Bedrooms, 1 Full Bathroom, Kitchen, Living Room and Family Room. The Living Room, Framily Room and Kitchen feature ceramic tile floors while the Bedrooms have wood laminate flooring and ceiling fans. One of the bedrooms is currently being used as an oversized closet. Separate Laundry/Utility Room is located off the Kitchen. There's plenty of entertaining space in the back yard which is enclosed by privacy fence. Lot size is 60 x 100. The exterior of the home is concrete block and the shingle roof was replaced in 2016. New AC and duct work 2021. The electrical panel was upgraded in 2017. Refrigerator, D/W and Oven with built-in Air-fryer are less than a year old.  Ring doorbell conveys. Perfect starter home for a small family or for a couple looking for a single story home. Home Warranty available with full price offer.
